            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="row g-4">
                    <div class="col-12">
                        <div class="service-content-inner d-flex align-items-center bg-white border border-primary rounded p-4 ps-0">
                            <div class="service-icon p-4">
                                <i class="fa fa-globe fa-4x text-primary"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="service-content">
                                <h5 class="mb-4">Kid-Friendly Wonderland</h5>
                                <p class="mb-0">
                                    Designed with imagination and safety in mind, our kid-friendly wonderland ensures that children have a blast while parents can relax knowing their little ones are entertained 
                                    in a secure environment
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12">
                        <div class="service-content-inner d-flex align-items-center bg-white border border-primary rounded p-4 ps-0">
                            <div class="service-icon p-4">
                                <i class="fa fa-hotel fa-4x text-primary"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="service-content">
                                <h5 class="mb-4">Supervised Fun</h5>
                                <p class="mb-0">
                                    Safety is our top priority, which is why our play area is supervised by attentive staff members trained to ensure a safe and enjoyable experience for all children. Parents can 
                                    rest assured knowing that their kids are under the watchful eye of our trained professionals
                                </p>
                            </div>
