                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Play Area Benefits -->
<section>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-top-border">
            <div class="mx-auto text-center mb-5" style="max-width: 900px;">
                <h5 class="section-title px-3">Play Area</h5>
                <h1 class="mb-0">Play Area Benefits</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="single-defination">
                        <h4 class="mb-20">Story Time</h4>
                        <p>
                            As the sun sets and the day's adventures draw to a close, the kids' play area transforms into a cozy retreat where families gather for evening storytelling sessions and movie nights under the
                            stars. With plush cushions and bean bags scattered across the floor, children snuggle up with their newfound friends
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="single-defination">
                        <h4 class="mb-20">Scavenger Hunts</h4>
                        <p>
                            Beyond the confines of the play area, thrilling scavenger hunts beckon adventurous souls to embark on captivating journeys throughout the resort grounds. Armed with maps and clues, young
                            explorers set out on exhilarating quests, uncovering hidden treasures
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="single-defination">
                        <h4 class="mb-20">Finger Painting For All</h4>
                        <p>
                            At the heart of the play area, a dedicated arts and crafts corner awaits, where young Picasso's and budding artisans can unleash their creativity onto blank canvases. With a plethora
                            of supplies at their fingertips – from vibrant paints and brushes to an assortment of crafting materials
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

